>> title: Next to Last Word
>> tags: gin,coupe,shaken,last-word

Chill a #coupe{} in the freezer.

Fill a #cocktail shaker{} with @ice{}.

Add @lemon juice{3/4%oz}, @elderflower liqueur{3/4%oz}, @maraschino liqueur{3/4%oz}, and @gin{3/4%oz}.

Shake for at least 30 seconds.

Serve in #coupe{}, garnish with @lemon twist{1}.